/outputs/

# Agent / personal working notes (not for public GitHub)
/docs/PROJECT.md
/docs/HANDOVER.md
/docs/HANDOVER_paper_consolidation.md

# Superseded root-level artifacts
/archive/

# Claude Code / Cursor local worktrees (keep machine-specific state out of git)
.claude/

# Office / LibreOffice lock files
**/~$*
.~lock.*

# Claude Code local state (keep .claude/settings.json, ignore transient/user-local)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
